{"tid":1418104,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打同我一樣都好灰","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:32:58.000Z","uid":155320,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a57ad9506d68e0795ff4c3a1b8b031b757cd41","tid":1418104,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:20.000Z","msg":"我已經try to be positive...<br />\n同女朋友傾電話又要扮到冇野<br />\n但實情我發夢發到好攰<br />\n唔撚敢諗今次輸左會點<br />\n2047香港會點 我既未來又係點<br />\n我只係20出頭既年輕人<br />\n我既未來到底係點樣<br />\n係香港又有冇未來<br />\n我睇唔透<br />\n<br />\n我呢一刻好撚亂<br />\n心靈上又亂 身體上又攰<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以教我點做<br />\n聽日又要返工<br />\n又要對住公司班港豚 雖然有D係明事理<br />\n但又DUM石又DUM磚 佢地一撚定又係到講三講四<br />\n每次聽撚到佢地咁講個人就好撚灰 唔撚想做野想屌柒佢地<br />\n<br />\n我睇唔到未來... 有冇巴打可以比個hug我<br />\n我好想喊"},{"pid":"e9c2e7c65ab1a3cecea314052e613130474612d6","tid":1418104,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a395e54ab20733dd2d0a73d55ac9ef9566a621","tid":1418104,"uid":275116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"不如休息1,2場<br />\n之後再企出黎呀<br />\n<br />\n你精神上攰比身體攰更嚴重"},{"pid":"ab7c85c2df6933e8f6cf5991faebbf242397481b","tid":1418104,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a395e54ab20733dd2d0a73d55ac9ef9566a621","tid":1418104,"uid":275116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"不如休息1,2場<br />\n之後再企出黎呀<br />\n<br />\n你精神上攰比身體攰更嚴重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:57:46.000Z","msg":"今日成個人都好似break down左...<br />\n做咩都冇撚哂心機....<br />\n但叫我唔留意我又好難做到.."},{"pid":"e503b730978ab3d3dddbcb8dc37dd2b81bc21aec","tid":1418104,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f6fb321d7ef566ab1ad1de4983229c0054e772","tid":1418104,"uid":258683,"like":0,"dis